1
00:01:08,239 --> 00:01:08,879
Doctor.

2
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:11,840
Brother.

3
00:01:12,200 --> 00:01:12,760
Are you okay?

4
00:01:26,560 --> 00:01:27,120
I'm fine.

5
00:01:27,920 --> 00:01:28,799
Family members, don't panic.

6
00:01:30,040 --> 00:01:31,200
It's just some bruising inside the mouth

7
00:01:31,439 --> 00:01:32,680
caused by the facial injury.

8
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:35,040
Just rinse with antiseptic

9
00:01:35,040 --> 00:01:35,719
mouthwash and he'll be fine.

10
00:01:36,799 --> 00:01:37,480
Thank goodness he's okay.

11
00:01:38,319 --> 00:01:38,879
Thank you, Doctor.

12
00:01:40,239 --> 00:01:40,760
Doctor.

13
00:01:40,959 --> 00:01:42,280
Please give him another check-up.

14
00:01:43,280 --> 00:01:44,519
The patient's life is not in danger.

15
00:01:45,040 --> 00:01:46,159
You shouldn't worry too much.

16
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:47,760
It might affect the patient's mood.

17
00:01:48,480 --> 00:01:49,040
Get some good rest.

18
00:01:49,879 --> 00:01:50,560
Okay, thank you, Doctor.

19
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:51,200
Thank you, Doctor.

20
00:01:52,480 --> 00:01:53,040
How are you feeling?

21
00:01:56,040 --> 00:01:57,519
I even saw the light.

22
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:58,799
You're hurt this badly

23
00:01:59,519 --> 00:02:00,280
and you're still cracking jokes.

24
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:01,200
Here.

25
00:02:01,359 --> 00:02:02,000
Cover yourself up properly.

26
00:02:04,079 --> 00:02:04,879
Feeling better?

27
00:02:13,120 --> 00:02:13,479
Hey.

28
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,080
What are you doing?

29
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:17,680
Your husband's right next to you.

30
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:18,560
Can't you see?

31
00:02:19,439 --> 00:02:20,520
Who's as carefree as you?

32
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:22,680
Is the Plot 7 General Contracting settled?

33
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:25,680
Only a few firms can handle

34
00:02:25,680 --> 00:02:26,719
the General Contracting for Plot 7.

35
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:27,919
Do they really have a choice?

36
00:02:28,879 --> 00:02:29,800
Don't get cocky too soon.

37
00:02:30,159 --> 00:02:31,120
If I hadn't taken a loss

38
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:32,199
and Xiao Yifan didn't want to compensate me,

39
00:02:32,439 --> 00:02:33,719
you never would've gotten this chance.

40
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:35,800
Right, right, right.

41
00:02:36,479 --> 00:02:38,400
It's all thanks to my Honey.

42
00:02:45,879 --> 00:02:46,360
Boss Fang.

43
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:48,159
He Junjie isn't dead.

44
00:02:48,599 --> 00:02:51,680
Plot 7 General Contracting bid is void.

45
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:54,439
What's wrong?

46
00:02:55,919 --> 00:02:56,639
Shut up.

47
00:02:59,439 --> 00:03:00,759
Are you crazy?

48
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:02,439
What's gotten into you now?

49
00:03:11,199 --> 00:03:12,199
Have an orange.

50
00:03:22,080 --> 00:03:22,800
We're here.

51
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:24,039
You're here.

52
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,280
You're still laughing.

53
00:03:31,479 --> 00:03:32,439
You scared us half to death.

54
00:03:32,919 --> 00:03:33,599
What's to be scared of?

55
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,199
I'm the one who saw the light.

56
00:03:35,319 --> 00:03:36,159
Not you.

57
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:39,599
You have a severe concussion,

58
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:40,919
broken ribs,

59
00:03:41,199 --> 00:03:42,199
and coughed up blood this morning.

60
00:03:42,759 --> 00:03:44,159
Now, from head to toe,

61
00:03:44,439 --> 00:03:45,599
the only thing working is your mouth.

62
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:46,560
I know.

63
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:48,159
My dear Brother,

64
00:03:48,879 --> 00:03:50,080
what tasty treats did you bring me?

65
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:51,120
Let me have a taste.

66
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:52,199
The doctor said...

67
00:03:52,199 --> 00:03:53,680
He can only eat light food.

68
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:55,319
Then how about

69
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:56,719
some seafood porridge?

70
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:57,599
Sure.

71
00:03:58,080 --> 00:03:58,599
I'll go get it.

72
00:03:59,199 --> 00:03:59,879
Wait a moment.

73
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:02,960
I need to talk to you.

74
00:04:07,759 --> 00:04:08,400
Go ahead.

75
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:11,280
I have a recording of Fang Bing on my phone.

76
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:13,719
I think he's the one trying to kill me.

77
00:04:16,639 --> 00:04:17,360
I suspect him too.

78
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:19,879
But the police already said

79
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:22,319
the driver is fully at fault.

80
00:04:22,879 --> 00:04:23,879
There's no way it's just a coincidence.

81
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:29,600
That car came straight at me.

82
00:04:31,079 --> 00:04:32,240
In that moment, I felt like I'd

83
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,279
already left this earth.

84
00:04:34,519 --> 00:04:35,040
Stay calm.

85
00:04:35,199 --> 00:04:36,120
Think it through carefully.

86
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:37,519
Are there any other suspicious points?

87
00:04:41,519 --> 00:04:42,560
Gather all the materials

88
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:43,759
from the companies involved

89
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:44,920
in Fang Bing's bid rigging,

90
00:04:45,279 --> 00:04:46,199
and return them all.

91
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:48,560
Make a big show of returning them.

92
00:04:50,439 --> 00:04:51,600
All right, Brother.

93
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:52,959
Rest up and recover.

94
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:54,079
Wait till I'm back.

95
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:56,279
Get me meat porridge from our usual spot.

96
00:04:56,439 --> 00:04:57,240
Make it savory.

97
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:00,160
Yifan.

98
00:05:00,759 --> 00:05:01,879
The doctor said he can only

99
00:05:01,879 --> 00:05:02,839
eat light food.

100
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:04,160
Just buy him

101
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,040
whatever's simple.

102
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:07,199
Honey,

103
00:05:07,519 --> 00:05:08,480
I'm the patient here.

104
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:10,480
You're impossible.

105
00:05:10,839 --> 00:05:11,519
So dramatic.

106
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:12,399
Rest up.

107
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:13,360
I'll go buy it.

108
00:05:13,879 --> 00:05:14,480
Thanks for the trouble.

109
00:05:17,879 --> 00:05:18,360
Baili.

110
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:20,560
You haven't slept for two days and nights.

111
00:05:20,839 --> 00:05:21,839
I'm worried about your health.

112
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:23,240
How about you leave Junjie

113
00:05:23,319 --> 00:05:24,439
to me and Yifan?

114
00:05:24,959 --> 00:05:25,959
Go home and get some rest.

115
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:26,720
It's fine.

116
00:05:27,199 --> 00:05:28,199
If I'm here taking care of him,

117
00:05:28,199 --> 00:05:29,160
I feel more at ease.

118
00:05:29,439 --> 00:05:30,199
It's just...

119
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:31,800
I'm a bit worried about the kid.

120
00:05:32,519 --> 00:05:33,040
Xiao Hui,

121
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:35,439
could you take Yuchen to your place

122
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,160
and look after him for a few days?

123
00:05:37,199 --> 00:05:37,759
No problem.

124
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:39,079
Don't worry.

125
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:40,000
I'll go pick him up right now.

126
00:05:40,519 --> 00:05:41,319
Stop worrying, okay?

127
00:05:41,879 --> 00:05:42,480
Sorry for the trouble.

128
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:44,199
Off to pick up your brother.

129
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:46,680
Bye, drive safe.

130
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,360
Lili, I'm leaving.

131
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:49,959
Okay, drive safe.

132
00:05:56,360 --> 00:05:57,279
We had a deal back then.

133
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:58,839
And we did everything

134
00:05:58,839 --> 00:05:59,759
exactly the way you wanted.

135
00:06:00,279 --> 00:06:01,040
But now we've been

136
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:02,399
notified we're disqualified.

137
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:04,000
What the hell are you playing at?

138
00:06:04,279 --> 00:06:05,000
Exactly.

139
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:06,639
Back then, Boss Fang

140
00:06:06,639 --> 00:06:07,800
promised us

141
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:08,480
five million.

142
00:06:08,879 --> 00:06:09,279
So what's it gonna be?

143
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:10,680
Cash or check?

144
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:15,319
Enough!

145
00:06:16,959 --> 00:06:18,000
You bunch of useless idiots.

146
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:20,519
He Junjie of Plot 7 General Contracting,

147
00:06:20,519 --> 00:06:21,519
is now lying in a hospital bed.

148
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:23,000
What are you whining to me for?

149
00:06:23,319 --> 00:06:24,879
Why do we care if he's in the hospital?

150
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:26,279
We followed your instructions

151
00:06:26,279 --> 00:06:27,160
step by step.

152
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:28,759
Now it's all ruined.

153
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:30,240
Who else should we go to?

154
00:06:30,319 --> 00:06:31,480
This whole thing now

155
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:32,560
isn't up to me anymore.

156
00:06:33,079 --> 00:06:34,000
You're saying this now?

157
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:35,120
Then you shouldn't have forced us

158
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:36,600
to tie our interests to yours.

159
00:06:36,759 --> 00:06:38,920
You think your crappy little companies

160
00:06:39,319 --> 00:06:40,600
could ever win the bid?

161
00:06:42,199 --> 00:06:43,120
At least we could get

162
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:44,040
a piece of the pie

163
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:44,959
from the General Contracting.

164
00:06:45,079 --> 00:06:46,000
With a project this big,

165
00:06:46,160 --> 00:06:47,920
even a small share brings in profit.

166
00:06:48,279 --> 00:06:49,160
And now?

167
00:06:49,519 --> 00:06:50,319
What can I do?

168
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:52,040
Kidnap the guy for you,

169
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:53,360
and make him sign a contract with you?

170
00:06:55,879 --> 00:06:56,759
Taking someone's livelihood

171
00:06:56,959 --> 00:06:58,000
is like killing their parents.

172
00:06:58,480 --> 00:07:00,000
Mr. Fang, Boss Fang,

173
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:01,439
how can you just swallow this?

174
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:05,639
Get out!

175
00:07:06,279 --> 00:07:07,000
All of you, get the hell out!

176
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:25,199
Go bring Old Xia and his wife over here.

177
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:29,600
Yo.

178
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:30,720
You haven't been here in a while.

179
00:08:30,759 --> 00:08:31,519
Boss.

180
00:08:31,560 --> 00:08:32,559
Stew this up for me.

181
00:08:32,639 --> 00:08:33,720
To help my buddy recover.

182
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:34,960
You got it, no problem.

183
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:44,759
I'll stew it right up.

184
00:09:06,399 --> 00:09:07,480
Mr. Xiao.

185
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:14,919
Have a seat.

186
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:20,679
Li Yao,

187
00:09:21,159 --> 00:09:22,559
you seem to have something on your mind.

188
00:09:25,159 --> 00:09:25,840
No, nothing.

189
00:09:26,799 --> 00:09:28,399
Then why do you look so pale?

190
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:30,879
Really, it's nothing.

191
00:09:36,759 --> 00:09:37,480
Li Yao,

192
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:41,639
even though you left our company,

193
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:42,919
but seven years ago,

194
00:09:42,919 --> 00:09:44,000
when you took the fall,

195
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:49,600
we all knew the truth.

196
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:07,840
Mr. Xiao,

197
00:10:08,159 --> 00:10:09,440
That really wasn't my intention.

198
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,519
I didn't want it to happen.

199
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:12,279
What happened to you,

200
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:14,759
I went through the same thing before.

201
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:16,240
The only difference is,

202
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:18,360
I had a Master.

203
00:10:18,919 --> 00:10:19,960
He taught me

204
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:22,559
to always stay true to yourself,

205
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:23,840
and never stray from the right path.

206
00:10:24,679 --> 00:10:28,039
But you made a huge mistake.

207
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:32,279
Mr. Xiao,

208
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:34,240
who is your Master?

209
00:10:39,879 --> 00:10:41,120
Back then,

210
00:10:42,240 --> 00:10:43,360
I was just a rookie.

211
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:01,480
Brothers,

212
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:03,679
it's too hot. Put it down, put it down.

213
00:11:03,919 --> 00:11:05,000
Let's go grab a drink.

214
00:11:06,399 --> 00:11:07,480
It's way too hot.

215
00:11:14,759 --> 00:11:15,679
Where are you guys going?

216
00:11:16,600 --> 00:11:17,440
It's too hot out.

217
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:19,000
We're going for a drink.

218
00:11:20,039 --> 00:11:20,840
The work we were assigned

219
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:21,559
isn't even finished yet.

220
00:11:21,799 --> 00:11:22,879
How can you just leave?

221
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:24,080
Take your time and do it yourself.

222
00:11:24,159 --> 00:11:26,200
Brothers, let's go.

223
00:12:13,559 --> 00:12:14,519
Yifan.

224
00:12:14,519 --> 00:12:16,639
You can't just push through it all alone.

225
00:12:18,519 --> 00:12:19,240
Have some water.

226
00:12:23,360 --> 00:12:24,080
Here.

227
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:25,080
Acting up again.

228
00:12:27,320 --> 00:12:29,279
Such a huge construction site,

229
00:12:29,279 --> 00:12:30,399
can you finish it all by yourself?

230
00:12:30,879 --> 00:12:32,919
As on-site managers,

231
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:34,720
managing people is what matters most.

232
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:37,399
Quality, progress, safety,

233
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:39,559
are all essential for us engineers.

234
00:12:39,879 --> 00:12:41,399
Do your work with full responsibility,

235
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:43,720
and live with full integrity.

236
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:46,799
Understood, Master.

237
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:47,879
All right.

238
00:12:48,679 --> 00:12:49,519
Take a break.

239
00:13:00,879 --> 00:13:02,840
So you've been bullied before too.

240
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:05,679
But at least you had a good Master.

241
00:13:06,440 --> 00:13:07,559
I didn't.
